<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>{{title}}</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background-color: #1a1a2e;
            color: #fff;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #0f3460;
        }
        header h1 {
            color: #00d4ff;
            font-size: 24px;
        }
        nav a {
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin-right: 20px;
            font-size: 18px;
        }
        nav a:hover {
            color: #00d4ff;
        }
        .container {
            padding: 20px;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: auto;
            text-align: center;
        }
        h2 {
            color: #fff;
            font-size: 28px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        p {
            color: #b0b0b0;
            font-size: 16px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        button {
            background-color: #00d4ff;
            color: #1a1a2e;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            font-size: 18px;
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            border-radius: 5px;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        button:hover {
            background-color: #00b2d4;
        }
        footer {
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding: 10px 0;
            text-align: center;
            background-color: #0f3460;
            color: #fff;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

{{>header }}

<div class="container">
    <h2>Zona creada con éxito</h2>
    <p>La nueva zona ha sido dada de alta correctamente.</p>

    <a href="/zonas"><button>Volver a la lista de zonas</button></a>
</div>

<footer>
    © 2024 Siemens. All rights reserved.
</footer>

</body>
</html>
